<view class="page-shell"><view class="custom-nav" style="padding-top: {{navTop}}px; height: {{navHeight}}px;"><view class="back-button" bindtap="goBack"><image src="{{icons.back}}" mode="aspectFit" /></view><text>成长报告预览</text></view><scroll-view class="page-scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}"><view style="height: {{navSpacer}}px;"></view><view class="content"><view class="page-heading"><text>家长成长报告预览</text><text>预览报告内容，确认后将发送给家长</text></view><view class="student-hero"><image src="{{avatar}}" mode="aspectFill" /><view><text>林浩</text><text>U10提高班</text><text>◷ 07-20 20:30　·　1号场</text></view><view class="basketball-mark"></view></view><view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">◉ 成长表现</view><view class="performance-row" wx:for="{{performances}}" wx:key="title"><view class="performance-icon">{{item.symbol}}</view><view><text>{{item.title}}</text><text>{{item.caption}}</text></view><view><text>{{item.score}}<text>/5</text></text><text>{{item.stars}}</text></view></view></view><view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">★ 成长亮点</view><view class="highlight-grid"><text wx:for="{{highlights}}" wx:key="*this">{{item}}</text></view></view><view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">💡 教练建议</view><text class="suggestion">继续保持积极的训练态度，在对抗中更主动地创造机会，加强弱侧移动与传球选择，提升比赛阅读能力。</text></view><view class="section-card"><view class="section-title">➤ 发送设置</view><view class="send-row"><text>🟢 家长微信</text><text>微信发送　›</text></view><view class="send-row"><text>◷ 发送时间</text><text>立即发送　›</text></view></view><view class="bottom-actions"><button bindtap="goBack">返回修改</button><button bindtap="send">确认发送</button></view><view class="safe-space"></view></view></scroll-view></view>
